title: Practical Randomness via Dual Contract
author: Yao-Chieh Hu (@yhuag) <yhuag@connect.ust.hk>, Ting-Ting Lee (@tina1998612) <tleeae@connect.ust.hk>
status: Draft
type: Standards Track
